eration</li> </ol>"},{"location":"protocol/level-0/#mathematical-foundation","title":"Mathematical Foundation","text":"<p>\u03c6 = (1 + \u221a5) / 2 \u03bb = ln(2) / \u03c6</p> <p>text</p>"},{"location":"registry/","title":"Sovereign Registry","text":"<p>DOI: 10.5281/ZENODO.18665294</p>"},{"location":"registry/#registered-marks","title":"Registered Marks","text":"Mark Hash Timestamp MNZ-001 sha256:... 2026-03-09 MNZ-002 sha256:... 2026-03-09"},{"location":"registry/#verification","title":"Verification","text":"<p>To verify a sovereign mark: `powershell .\\Verify-Mark.ps1 -Mark [HASH]</p>"}]}